  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the hot pot vessel over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion, garlic, and ginger, and saute until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the mustard seeds and berbere spice, and stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chicken broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Add the pappardelle pasta, cover the vessel, and pressure-cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Release the pressure, and stir in the mustard seeds and berbere spice.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs if desired."
